<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Password Reset OTP</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width:600px; margin:0 auto; padding:20px;">
  <h2 style="color:#0f766e;">Your OTP Code</h2>
  <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
  <p>Your one-time password (OTP) for password reset is:</p>
  <div style="font-size:28px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:2px; color:#0d9488; margin:14px 0;">{{otp}}</div>
  <p>This code expires in {{expiresMinutes}} minutes.</p>
  <p style="margin-top:20px; color:#6b7280; font-size:12px;">If you did not request this, you can ignore this email.</p>
</body>
</html>

